I made a font! 😳 AA Penny Available now in my store! Super 70s vibes with tonnns of swash alternates and a full glyph set. Worked really hard on this with the help of @wayne.pdf It’s inspired by the font Marvin I stumbled onto on @fonts.in.use I expanded it and added new swashes and cleaned things up for max usability. So excited for you to mess around with this, tag me in any designs you make I wanna see what you do with it and will be sharing my faves!! The name Penny comes from my late family dog who brought me so much joy so this is a little homage to her I hope it brings you some joy too 💕🥹

If you haven’t heard I dropped a new font called Penny! 🕺In the spirit of its quirkiness and boldness here are some minimal designs about being yourself regardless of what others think 😼 (Grab Penny in my store now!)
These are very real photos I took of people using Penny out in the wild on a recent road trip🚙 The font is available in my store now if you want to try it yourself!

The bootleg remix that started my artistic journey is finally officially coming out!  I discovered the original track in the summer of 2013.  Uploaded the remix to SoundCloud and it caught fire with over 3M streams.  I’m here today because of this song.  Thank you @thelighthouseandthewhaler for making this a reality. “Venice Remix” is out everywhere April 28th, pre-save link in bio!

Venice Remix OUT NOW!  I (Andrey) made this remix in 2015 when I used to call them Dreymixes and tried to get @thelighthouseandthewhaler attention… swipe to see all my posts from 2015.  8 years later we finally made it happen! This track started my entire creative journey, without it, I wouldn’t be here. Link in bio!

Golden Hour with @hanswilliams is out a week from today! I watched that movie Nice Guys a few years ago and immediately was inspired to make something that felt cinematic and 70s. I sent it to Hans who came back with some of my favorite songwriting to date, about wasted youth and self love. Fast forward to now and this song has inspired this entire EP and I’m so excited for you guys to hear it, I hope it resonates with and inspires you 🌅

Golden Hour with @Hanswilliams is out now! 3 years in the making, this one’s special. Hope it’s the perfect soundtrack to the end of your summer, swipe to see our first time performing an early version at our sold out nyc show! 🌅

Supergraphic Ultramodern. A big picture look at life in modern times. I wanted to create a project that captured what it felt like to be alive today. Musically it’s a new chapter for me, creating something grandiose, but personal. Massive thanks to the incredible artists I was able to work with to give this project life: @kinfu__ @hanswilliams @itsbabyjake @felly @eboneedavis I started the first song “Golden Hour” 3 years ago, the process of getting this music to the level I wanted was tough - add in all the creative and visuals and I was definitely in over my head 😭. A lot of highs and lows, failures and lessons went into this, but I’m so excited that it’s finally out and you get to experience it. Definitely would recommend listening front to back for the full experience. Thank you thank you thank you everyone who helped me get to this point and thank you everyone who follows and listens 🖤

PS. The visuals for the song’s will be coming out over the next few weeks. “Chasing Daylight” Visual is out now!!

The “A New World” video with @eboneedavis is OUT TOMORROW AT 1PM ET / 10AM PT.  I can’t speak more highly about Ebonee.  She is a true artist and was incredibly kind enough to let me put my music to such a powerful poem. More on this tomorrow.  Can’t wait for you guys to see this.

The “A New World” video with @eboneedavis is OUT NOW (link in bio). The most powerful song I’ve been a part of, written by Ebonee.  What a privilege this is to be able to share a part in delivering her message.  In Ebonee’s words - “A New World” is a battle cry, signaling the impending changes that will ripple across our nation as we ascend into the next dimension of our humanity. For centuries we have endured grueling lives under the thumb of oppression and exploitation while navigating broken systems. It is now time for the spiritual sickness that has plagued America to be unveiled and washed away so that ‘A New World’ can be born — one that is in alignment with nature and values life. In order for this shift to occur collectively, each of us must be accountable for interrogating our individual programming and purging the sickness within, thus reclaiming our personal power.”

Supergraphic design pack is here! From this crazy emboss template i’ve spent literally over a year honing to 33 of my fave textures: talking wax paper, tracing paper, vintage mags, dusty plastic, and even my wall. These crazy useful illustrator brushes that i’ve been using in recent work, font pairing guide and video tutorials for all of it to wrap it up! Keeping it affordable considering the value you’re getting as always to show my appreciation for all of you. I’m so hype to see what you all do with these assets, pleeease use the emboss on cover art 🥹🖤 LINK IN BIO! If you share this post i’ll love u 4ever 🫶
